defmodule Solution do
  @spec min_changes(s :: String.t) :: integer
  def min_changes(s) do
    Enum.reduce(Enum.with_index(s), {0, 0}, fn {char, idx}, {zero_changes, one_changes} ->
      if rem(idx, 2) == 0 do
        {zero_changes + if(char == '1', do: 1, else: 0), one_changes + if(char == '0', do: 1, else: 0)}
      else
        {zero_changes + if(char == '0', do: 1, else: 0), one_changes + if(char == '1', do: 1, else: 0)}
      end
    end)
    |> Tuple.to_list()
    |> Enum.min()
  end
end
